title: Elisha Cuthbert
itunes:title: Elisha Cuthbert
itunes:subtitle: ELISHA CUTHBERT (The Girl Next Door, 24, Happy Endings, The Ranch) joins Anna to discuss having actress friends, challenges of the sitcom format, the importance of knowing how to BBQ, first love heartbreak and racing horses with the family Astro Van. Anna
description:
In this episode...

- Karate vs. acting
- Competing for The Girl Next Door
- Having actress friends
- Blonde vs. brunette
- The challenges of sitcom
- How to be funny
- Being pregnant
- Dealbreakers
- The importance of knowing how to BBQ
- Red carpet with Beige
- Friendship dealbreakers
- First love heartbreak
- Brad asks Elisha to prom
- Eating apples
- Old school publicity vs. social media
- Racing horses with the family Astro Van
- Advice to callers Kayla and Lindsay
